name: Tetilla aligns with Sandia as Tom surveys the view
Nearing the North peak, hill designations get confusing.
Sangre de Cristos highlight the scenery
Numerous lava peaks dot the landscape here
A hogback ridge points the way back
Natures beauty infiltrates every part of the desert landscape
Bushwhacking the way back from the peaks
A peak around the stone ridge to asses our return path
